Rubric-Entry-Formatter-KwikiFormatish

This is a plugin to allow the use of Kwiki-like formatting in Rubric entry
bodies.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

